        <mxCell id="MmzZZRzJVWttOzWb7i2U-57" value="User-Data Bootstrap :&#xa;1. apt install nodejs/npm/mysql-client/jq&#xa;2. Install AWS CLI v2&#xa;3. Download &amp; extract code.zip&#xa;4. npm install aws-sdk&#xa;5. Fetch secret rds-app-secret (retry ×20)&#xa;6. Wait MySQL ready (retry ×20)&#xa;7. CREATE USER nodeapp / DB STUDENTS&#xa;8. npm start :80 (env vars injectées)" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;fillColor=#e8f5e9;strokeColor=#388E3C;fontSize=8;align=left;spacingLeft=6;" vertex="1" parent="1">
